  ('medical-tech-moex-11948', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-102-bccd9a5a', 'sub-medical-tech-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列關於多烯（Polyene）類抗黴菌藥物之敘述，何者錯誤？', '["多烯（Polyene）分子會聚合起來嵌入細胞膜中，造成細胞膜破洞使細胞質內物質流失", "Amphotericin B與Nystatin屬此類", "Nystatin由於易被腸胃吸收，因此較少用於治療腸胃道黴菌感染", "Amphotericin B常用於全身性黴菌感染之治療"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:44+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "0770013e9b2e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a3e37902d519", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102100", "c": "311", "s": "44", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "微生物學與臨床微生物學（包括細菌與黴菌）", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年第二次專技牙醫師分試藥師醫事檢驗師醫放師助產師物理治療師職能治療師呼吸治療師獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 61, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
