  ('medical-tech-moex-11950', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-102-bccd9a5a', 'sub-medical-tech-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列關於抗生素感受性試驗之敘述，何者錯誤？', '["使用培養液稀釋法或瓊脂稀釋法皆可，視細菌生長特性而定", "判讀標準可劃分為感受（susceptible）、中間型（intermediate）或抵抗（resistant）三種", "MIC小於或等於區分點（breakpoint）濃度可歸為感受性（susceptible）", "同一種抗生素對不同微生物之區分點（breakpoint）濃度皆相同"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:44+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "0770013e9b2e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a3e37902d519", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102100", "c": "311", "s": "44", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "微生物學與臨床微生物學（包括細菌與黴菌）", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年第二次專技牙醫師分試藥師醫事檢驗師醫放師助產師物理治療師職能治療師呼吸治療師獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 63, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
